{"tid":1188011,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尷尬了，利物浦曼聯主場沒大屏幕，無法進行VAR回放","createTime":"2019-06-06T04:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T14:02:14.000Z","uid":30768,"like":66,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"1609d60fb7afa2c5b2028e3efb5db9c53a85698b","tid":1188011,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:02:34.000Z","msg":"英超VAR推行了新規定，將在球場大屏幕內對VAR判定的結果進行回放，這樣裁判的判罰對現場球迷來說更為透明。但英超兩支老牌豪門曼聯和利物浦將成為唯二兩個主場沒有大屏幕、無法進行回放的球隊。<br />\n<br />\n目前英超的20支球隊中，晏菲路和奧托福是唯一兩個沒有大屏幕的體育場，這也意味著，如果事情沒有改變，利物浦和曼聯的球迷們將無法從主場收看VAR的回放。不過據悉英足總方面也在考慮其他的途徑，如App的使用也在考慮範圍內。<br />\n<br />\n我哋曼聯會唔會因為咁無得重奪英超草皮王<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c9854cf1c5d39403fc2b03e2aa384887a1bfc6","tid":1188011,"uid":5649,"like":72,"dislike":4,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:03:52.000Z","msg":"兩隊黑哨波以行動反VAR"},{"pid":"10a62a0271b8c35999a5b8dce1126f227e4ff247","tid":1188011,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eed70911d05e85bd14c346fae465e2c62cf53ef","tid":1188011,"uid":60695,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:05:12.000Z","msg":"英超螢幕獎"},{"pid":"37b7328caddbf25dd04c6ba11fda827434a3a7cf","tid":1188011,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:05:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc2581df3826a10342cfe5e59331b9681c39e23","tid":1188011,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:05:46.000Z","msg":"最佳螢幕大獎"},{"pid":"50542a100581e9ae7e20ff48a7094263b8ac45b1","tid":1188011,"uid":46849,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"1609d60fb7afa2c5b2028e3efb5db9c53a85698b","tid":1188011,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"201